---
layout: base.njk
title: Exploring the Timeless Wisdom of Hindu Philosophy
description: Discover core concepts in Hindu philosophy that continue to shape thought, culture, and spirituality worldwide.
---

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero">
  <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Core Concepts in Hindu Philosophy" class="hero-image">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <span class="eyebrow">Philosophical Wisdom</span>
    <h1>Core Concepts in Hindu Philosophy</h1>
    <p>Explore the timeless principles that shape understanding, consciousness, and the human experience.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">
        Get in Touch
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
      </a>
      <a href="#about" class="btn btn-ghost">
        Learn More
        <span class="arrow">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- About -->
<section id="about" class="alt-bg">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-text">
        <span class="eyebrow">Author</span>
        <h2>A Journey Through Philosophical Inquiry</h2>
        <p>This exploration of core concepts in Hindu philosophy draws from centuries of wisdom, bridging ancient thought with contemporary understanding. The author brings a scholarly perspective combined with accessible insights to make these profound ideas relevant to modern seekers.</p>
        <p>From the fundamental concepts of Brahman and Atman to the practical ethics of karma and dharma, each principle is examined with depth and clarity, offering readers a comprehensive introduction to one of the world's oldest and richest philosophical traditions.</p>
        <p>Whether you're a scholar, student, or curious learner, this book provides valuable frameworks for understanding consciousness, morality, and the nature of reality itself.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">
          Connect with the Author
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="about-image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573497019418-b400bb3ab074?w=1600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Author exploring Hindu philosophy concepts">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Services -->
<section id="services">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">What's Included</span>
      <h2>Comprehensive Resources</h2>
      <p>Access author insights, detailed book information, and exclusive promotional content to deepen your understanding of Hindu philosophy.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-3">
      {% for service in services %}
      <div class="card scroll-reveal">
        <div class="card-image">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556761175-5973dc0f32e7?w=600&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="{{ service.alt }}">
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <h3>{{ service.name }}</h3>
          <p>{{ service.description }}</p>
          <a href="#contact" class="card-link">
            Learn More <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta-section alt-bg">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">Connect</span>
    <h2>Ready to Explore These Concepts?</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 2em; max-width: 680px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
      Get in touch to discuss the book, schedule author sessions, or arrange speaking engagements.
    </p>
    <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">
      Get in Touch
      <span class="arrow">→</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Contact -->
<section id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="eyebrow">Let's Talk</span>
      <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
      <p>Have questions about the book or interested in discussing Hindu philosophy? We'd love to hear from you.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-wrapper">
      <form class="contact-form" id="contact-form" method="POST">
        <div class="form-status"></div>
        
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="name">Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="subject">Subject</label>
          <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" placeholder="What is this about?" required>
        </div>

        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" required></textarea>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
          Send Message
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </button>
      </form>

      <div class="contact-info">
        <h3>Contact Information</h3>
        
        <div class="info-item">
          <strong>Email</strong>
          <a href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-item">
          <strong>Phone</strong>
          <a href="tel:{{ site.phone }}">{{ site.phone_display }}</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-item">
          <strong>Location</strong>
          <p>{{ site.address }}</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-item">
          <strong>WhatsApp</strong>
          <a href="https://wa.me/{{ site.phone | replace('+', '') }}?text={{ site.whatsapp_message | urlencode }}" target="_blank">
            Start a conversation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
